channel.title: [NEW] 667 Server "Nibiru"
channel.description:
Hello, so I used to be a big part in the RSPS industry. You may know me by the name 'Brian h'. Anyway, after quitting RSPS business for 3 years I'm back, and I'm creating a project It's gonna be big. I need a few serious people who are willing to put some work in with me to maximize this server out, because I plan to make this the BEST server out there. And of course bring back the RSPS community, I see it's fallen off alot. If there's anyone out there interested in joining in, or if you want more info just PM me here and I'll get back to you. Or just sign up on the temporary forum page here: http://w11.zetaboards.com/PlanetxNibiru/index/
[b]I need:[/b]
- 2 other developers besides myself - 2 moderators - A GFX artist - A forum developer and of course players, but there will be tons. ;) Thanks!
- Planet X Nibiru Owner.
